Package posparser

Provides a clean interface to perform NLP tokenisation using the grok library

          Description

Class Summary
DebugHandler An XML callback handler that does debugging output dumps to stdout of each of the tokens
GetPosDoc A Singleton that creates a default Pipeline using English preprocessed files and handles Exceptions.
POSWrapper A wrapper to start NLP parsing; converting the XML output to be interpreted by org.xml.(...)Handler callbacks.
